						<summary>

						<p>On a slab lying in front of the village school in the compound of Kalamēśvara temple.</p>						

						<p>Kannara.</p>						

						<p>It seems to register a gift to the god Kalidēva. As the inscription is much damaged, the date and other details are lost.</p>						

